---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Main from '../layouts/main.astro';
import DanielsPhoto from '/public/images/daniels.jpg';
import { Button } from '../components/ui/button';

// Full Astro Component Syntax:
// https://docs.astro.build/basics/astro-components/
---

<html lang="en">
	<Main>
		<section>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-x-0 md:gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 pt-4 md:pt-8 lg:pt-16">
			  <article>
				<h1 class="mb-1 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tighter">
				  Daniel Soliman
				</h1>
				<h4 class="mb-4 text-base text-neutral-700">Construction Planner and Front End Engineer</h4>
				<p class="mb-4">
					Hi, I’m Daniel, a construction planner and tech enthusiast with 20+ years of experience. I was the scheduler at the Marlins Ballpark, Brickell City Centre, LAX, and other condos, hospitals, and airports throughout Miami. I believe the key to a successful project is understanding priorities and how the plan works in a constantly changing environment.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
				  I'm currently the co-founder of 
				  <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://www.planflow.io"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
				  >
					Planflow</a>, a construction operations platform that helps construction teams
				  execute on schedule, improve productivity, and finish early.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
				  I also work at 
				  <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://www.robinsmorton.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
				  >Robins & Morton</a>, an ENR100 healthcare general contractor, managing multiple projects, including <a
				  class="underline"
				  href="https://www.robinsmorton.com/robins-morton-receives-project-of-the-year-at-synchro-software-digital-construction-awards/"
				  target="_blank"
				  rel="noopener noreferrer"
				>Project of the year
				</a>. I developed tools like <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://robinsmorton.gitbook.io/timetable-figjam"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
				  >
					TimeTable FigJam
				  </a>, 
				  <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://help.timetable.app/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
				  >
					TimeTable Visio
				  </a>
				  , 
				  <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://www.ctrlwiz.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
				  >
					CtrlWiz
				  </a>, <a
				  class="underline"
				  href="https://www.plusdelta.app"
				  target="_blank"
				  rel="noopener"
				>
				  PlusDelta
				</a>, <a
				  class="underline"
				  href="https://flypaper.com/slatplanner/"
				  target="_blank"
				  rel="noopener"
				>
				  SlatPlanner (acquired)</a>. With the time left, I train superintendents on CPM scheduling and administer Primavera Cloud for the company.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-4">
					Previously, I was the Director of BIM and Scheduling at <a
					class="underline"
					href="https://bakerconstruction.com/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
				  >
					Baker Concrete
				  </a>, where I started the BIM department and established scheduling standards.
				</p>
				<p>I’ve consulted for companies like Tesla, Hunt Construction (now AECOM), Telsa, US Navy, DoD, Turner Construction, Suffolk Construction, Americaribe (Bouygues), and Moriarty Florida.</p>
				<div class="my-8">
				  <!-- <BlogPosts /> -->
				</div>
			  </article>
			  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full gap-4 md:gap-8">
				<figure class="py-0.5 shrink-0">
				<img
				  class="rounded-full w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48"
				  src={DanielsPhoto.src}
				  alt="photo of Daniel Soliman"
				  loading="lazy"
				/></figure>
			  <Button variant={'social'}><a href="/cv_daniel_soliman.pdf" target="_blank">View my CV</a></Button>
			</div>
			</div>
		  </section>
	</Main>
</html>
